messages.message: Hi France, hope we can work together this game! Would you be up for running the WT?
Hey Germany! Just reaching out to say hello and to wish you luck! I think A/G is a great alliance, and hopefully you'll be able to get a three build year.
Burgundy is yours, I won't be hitting it.
Would be a strong start for it. Make sure you convince Italy not to attack you. Are you thinking about moving on Russia early?
I would be up for that if England agrees. I'm in! DMZ Bur? You could hold Mun if you want.
Hi Russia, best of luck this game. I won't move against you if you leave Austria alone and attack Turkey. Is this something you could agree to?
I won't be holding Munich.
Never mind. Let's take England!
That's the plan. It'll help if you give him Sweden :)
Ok!
Hi England, hope we can work together this game! What are your plans early?
Is England talking to you? They're not responding to me...
Hi Italy, best of luck this game! Are you working with Austria?
No, I just sent him a message.
Best of luck this game Turkey, make sure you convince Italy not to Lepanto!
